name: TandemX
description: TandemX is an application that builds groups of digital currencies that have similar behavior, like price evolution. The user can watch 3 groups of currencies, based on their behavior: ascending, flat, descending. In the next future, the users will be able to configure the application through a wide range of parameters. This application was created and is proudly provided within the SynergyCrowds project initiative.
